name: Urbosa
description:
The third take on this is probably the last release until we get new tech to make better models. I'm including multiple versions so make sure you read the release notes!

V3 should work on most every 1.5 model. The sweet spot seems to be around 0.7-0.9 for most models, but you can do between 0.3-1.4 usually depending on desired effect.

You may want to add some or all of the keywords to the prompt depending on which outfit you are trying to get her to wear.
